description: Welcome to your stunning bi-level penthouse in the heart of South Boston! This beautifully designed 2-bedroom, 1-bath home boasts a private roof deck perfect for entertaining while soaking in breathtaking city views. Step into the first level, where you'll find a living room featuring exposed brick that adds character and warmth. The first bedroom also showcases charming exposed brick, creating a cozy retreat. The second bedroom offers fantastic city views, making it ideal for relaxation and inspiration. Enjoy the convenience of an additional private outdoor space on the first level, perfect for morning coffee or evening unwind. The open-concept layout seamlessly blends indoor and outdoor living, creating a vibrant atmosphere for entertaining or quiet evenings at home. With its prime location, you'll be just moments away from South Boston’s finest dining, shopping, and parks. Don’t miss this rare opportunity to experience urban living at its finest in a beautiful penthouse sanctuary!
